title: Default Test Form
elements:
custom_option_autocomplete:
  '#type': webform_autocomplete
  '#title': 'Custom option autocomplete'
  '#autocomplete_items':
    - 'Blue moon'
    - 'Coors light'
    - Corona
multivalue_unlimited_predefined_options_autocomplete:
  '#type': webform_autocomplete
  '#title': 'Multivalue unlimited predefined options autocomplete'
  '#multiple': true
  '#autocomplete_items': employment_status
checked_by_default_checkbox:
  '#type': checkbox
  '#title': 'Checked by default checkbox'
  '#default_value': true
composite_basic_address_with_some_default_values:
  '#type': webform_address
  '#title': 'Composite basic address with default values and required field'
  '#title_display': before
  '#default_value':
    address: ''
    address_2: ''
    city: ''
    state_province: 'New York'
    postal_code: ''
    country: 'United States'
  '#address__required': true
checkboxes_custom_value:
  '#type': checkboxes
  '#title': 'Checkboxes custom value with default'
  '#options':
    apple: apple
    banana: banana
    cherry: cherry
  '#default_value':
    - banana
radios_other_predefined_options:
  '#type': webform_radios_other
  '#title': 'Radios other predefined options'
  '#options': employment_status
select_custom_options:
  '#type': select
  '#title': 'Required select custom options'
  '#options':
    crunch: crunch
    'kit kat': 'kit kat'
    twix: twix
  '#required': true
conditional_helper_checkbox:
  '#type': checkbox
  '#title': 'Conditional helper checkbox'
conditional_helper_textfield:
  '#type': textfield
  '#title': 'Conditional helper textfield'
conditional_textarea:
  '#type': textarea
  '#title': 'Conditional textarea'
  '#states':
    disabled:
      - ':input[name="conditional_helper_checkbox"]':
          checked: true
      - or
      - ':input[name="checkboxes_custom_value[apple]"]':
          checked: true
    required:
      ':input[name="conditional_helper_textfield"]':
        value: req
container_multivalue_composite_basic_address:
  '#type': container
  multivalue_basic_address_inside_of_a_container:
    '#type': webform_address
    '#title': 'Multivalue basic address inside of a container'
    '#multiple': 3
  text_field_with_a_default_value_inside_container:
    '#type': textfield
    '#title': 'Text field with a default value inside container'
    '#states':
      disabled:
        ':input[name="custom_option_autocomplete"]':
          value: Corona
    '#default_value': 'I am a default value!'
table:
  '#type': webform_table
  '#title': Table
  table_01:
    '#type': webform_table_row
    '#title': 'Table row 1'
    table_01_textarea_in_table_row_1:
      '#type': textarea
      '#title': 'Textarea in table row 1'
    table_01_textfield_in_table_row_1:
      '#type': textfield
      '#title': 'Textfield in table row 1'
      '#required': true
      '#states':
        invisible:
          ':input[name="table_01_textarea_in_table_row_1"]':
            filled: true
  table_02:
    '#type': webform_table_row
    '#title': 'Table row 2'
    required_textarea_in_table_row_2:
      '#type': textarea
      '#title': 'Required textarea in table row 2'
      '#required': true
    multivalue_textfield_in_table_row_2:
      '#type': textfield
      '#title': 'Multivalue textfield in table row 2'
      '#multiple': 3
actions:
  '#type': webform_actions
  '#title': 'Submit button(s)'
